➜阿里云启动“数智化人才”万人招聘！海量阿里云职位来袭，更有面试直通机会
http://www.sohu.com/a/418782655_308467	29052
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/19f2640f35b8457ba438731eac6622a4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俗话说“金九银十”</p>
